race.comment: Tricky race. AUDIO BOY (4) continues to race well without winning, missing by 2.1L most recently. Getting onto the bigger Pinjarra circuit may help and he'll find this an easier race. Pike sticks and he can end his winning drought. ALL GRUNT (1) is running out of chances, though this presents as a great opportunity to return to form. Out to this trip may be what he's looking for and Noske reunites with the gelding. Best is good enough, he just needs to recapture that form. LATE ARRIVAL (2) is another who is racing well without winning in recent times. He wasn't far away over 2200m last week at Ascot and has the speed to offset the wide alley. Can roll forward and be tough to run down. LET SPARKS FLY (13) wasn't far away last start at Ascot and is unbeaten at this track and trip. This is tougher but she makes plenty of appeal with no weight on her back.
